---
title: Updating an advertising slot
endpoint: /advertising_units/slots/{id}
method: patch
---

Update an advertising slot's sponsor content and approval status.

## Approving content

To approve a slot's content, set `content_approved_at` to a datetime value. This will automatically clear any rejection status.

## Rejecting content

To reject a slot's content, set `content_rejection_reason` to explain why the content was rejected.
